room_title: Escape room "Magic Wonderland" by FLEE in Seattle
room_description:
You are the descendant of a long heritage line of treasure hunters. Your grandfather has always told you stories about "... the land with an incomplete mission". To fulfill his wish, you are going to search for this lost kingdom with a team of amateur cryptologists.
To track the traces of the lost kingdom, you've come a long way but you and your team were swept away and lost touch with each other. The journey will be arduous, and you will need the expertise of your team to cross difficult paths, travel to foreign lands, and discover hidden clues together to decode the final mystery. Will you be able to reunite with your team and complete the unfinished mission on your way out?
